column3: There's string changes already queued for 0.7 still... at least if you include JSON-RPC help (not sure if that's translated)\n

JSON-RPC stuff is not translated, so that should be no problem. My statement was primarily about the UI, and also command-line options, though those are less important to have translated so if one's added it doesn't matter...\n
